類 software大量問題 sensor spinout 用用下會自己飛咗去第到<br />\n<br />\nHyperx: 好似唔錯 幾實淨<br />\n<br />\n想搵返sensei shape可睇睇dream machine(<a href=\"http://us.maxgaming.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fus.maxgaming.com&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYlpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9dbffc38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">us.maxgaming.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\nroccat: 買過一次 同razer有得fight<br />\n<br />\nrazer: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自求多福"},{"pid":"ca9336aade952b85f909420eb24c04251f8a8063","tid":495224,"uid":18283,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T09:49:08.000Z","msg":"打撚到我嘔心瀝血 下次唔打了"},{"pid":"82129eb4a6b73b538b4e9c1e82f68d1d74efddc1","tid":495224,"uid":44192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:11:46.000Z","msg":"Fps 系列<br />\n<br />\n&gt; 18cm 長手掌：ec1a, rival 300, da chroma, fnatic flick, final mouse (性價比：rival, 最多人用：ec1a, 最強黑馬：finalmouse）<br />\n17-18cm：ec2a, g403 (用緊g403, 性價比最高係尼隻）<br />\n&lt; 17cm: g pro, g303, fk2 (建議g303 最抵玩)"},{"pid":"c69b4ae528c20801a581a589ee0f1eba6fa2a2fc","tid":495224,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T10:13:04.000Z","msg":"Watch this:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGJaDZC7PChgd-XMwcbZkiw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGJaDZC7PChgd-XMwcbZkiw&d=cz0NtoQHsL2naZ4LrITYlpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c181ef34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGJaDZC7PChgd-XMwcbZkiw</a>"},{"pid":"7202bb2cc1776ddf1d9bbe928cd453af900db4a4","tid":495224,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"嘩屌冇人講logi G pro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7017112a823cf0fd42382d57c42e401b40d5da1","tid":495224,"uid":18283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>